snippet: Same opponent, same old story for Milos Raonic but despite a sixth defeat of the year by Andy Murray at the ATP World Tour Finals on Saturday the Canadian underlined he will be a player to fear in 2017....
lead_paragraph: Same opponent, same old story for Milos Raonic but despite a sixth defeat of the year by Andy Murray at the ATP World Tour Finals on Saturday the Canadian underlined he will be a player to fear in 2017.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Proud of Year After Agonizing Defeat by Murray
headline.main: Raonic Proud of Year After Agonizing Defeat by Murray
